name: Paper Bag Head 000
description:
Who are these mysterious Paper Bag Heads? Can you help me find them?
With this NFT, you are enabled to let me create a custom Paper Bag Head for you. Please contact me via Twitter (@HeadsPaper) to discuss your Paper Bag Head. As soon as you burn Paper Bag Head 000 and send me the link to your operation (tzkt.io) via DM, I'll start working on your custom PBH. As soon as it is finished, I'll airdrop it directly to your wallet. Warning !! You need to discuss your NFT with me before we reach PBH 590! So if you don't contact me in time, I won't be able to create you a custom PBH.
